{"tid":119225,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"政府換屆之前，政府再出招壓抑樓市","createTime":"2017-02-13T14:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T09:46:01.000Z","uid":5584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b93eec5f6f9184e4cdf386af110cd72efe05606a","tid":119225,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:56:00.000Z","msg":"2月13日。特此存記錄<br />\n<br />\n我話既！政府在早前加稅變為15%後，效用已經減退。<br />\n<br />\n市民入市的意欲，不但沒有減少，反而因為（新樓）地產商把增加的成本轉介到消費者，故意越賣越貴，營造早買早享受，遲買貴幾舊效應。當然無知的市民照單全收，新樓越貴越好賣。<br />\n<br />\n好快好快，新樓市場會有井噴式上升風險。最慘係，一手樓盤會帶動二手樓盤價量齊升。<br />\n<br />\n所以新一輪辣招在所難免，最有可能在新招上面加入微調因素！！！！"},{"pid":"90574aae2ab41932a4c33fbadd3b2590a2060e18","tid":119225,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n689 為左證明自己係有撚用<br />\n<br />\n出招做低個樓價升勢,  再加上世界經濟環境因素,  樓價大跌<br />\n搞到下屆政府好似得罪左中產<br />\n<br />\n部處 5 年後又可以返嚟做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbdfd8374f3d3d0b96e50b178222ed893d0e1ee","tid":119225,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:59:37.000Z","msg":"炒家們，掃樓要快手了！！！"},{"pid":"8958a3651464cfe43caef281a6513957235c540d","tid":119225,"uid":14789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T20:09:45.000Z","msg":"起到個法案都過唔切立法會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係佢就會換多幾個心腹去做局長"},{"pid":"e7ac64e8a198f0b8fa1d864bd0df562fd5f9b063","tid":119225,"uid":63212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:10:01.000Z","msg":"再升"},{"pid":"b690d430de5f26726c0371214c737f12a7673ada","tid":119225,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起到個法案都過唔切立法會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor